						<summary>

						<p>A pillar lying in front of the same temple.</p>						

						<p>This inscription is in Veṭṭeḻuttu script.</p>						

						<p>It records a gift of two pillars (on one of which this inscription is engraved) by a certain Āmbalaṅkōḍaṉ of Śellūr in Muḻaiyu-nāḍu in Śōṇāḍu.</p>						

